QUESTIONS PREVIEW:
Q1. (a) Find the eigenvalues and eigenvectors of the matrix [[1, 2], [3, 2]].
    (b) Verify Cayley-Hamilton theorem for the matrix A = [[2, 1], [1, 2]].
Q2. (a) Evaluate the limit using L'Hospital's Rule: lim(x->0) (sin x - x) / x^3.
    (b) Expand e^x cos y in powers of x and y near (0, 0) up to second degree terms.
